<template>
    <NavBar/>
    <ChildOne @send="HandleSend"/>
    
    <ChildTwo/>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  import ChildOne from './ChildOne.vue'
  import ChildTwo from './ChildTwo.vue'
  import NavBar from './NavBar.vue'
  export default {
    name: 'HomePage',
    components:{
      ChildOne,
      ChildTwo,
      NavBar
    },
    data(){
      return{
    user: [],
    admin: [],
    name:"",
    age:"",
    role:"",
      } 
    },
    methods: {
      HandleSend(data){
        name = data[0];
        age = data[1];
        role = data[2];
        console.log(data);

      }
    },
  }
  </script>
